  levelPacks:
  - LevelNumber: 1
    LevelId: mahjong_story
    DisplayName: "Mahjong'a Ho\u015Fgeldiniz"
    Music: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 59d5dcc18fcdc02429813b0c0c1b8893, type: 3}
    Tiles:
    - Id: bamboo
      Prefab: {fileID: 6253049638512766740, guid: 515c0dc81470f48438fc80049419a56f, type: 3}
    - Id: sonsuz
      Prefab: {fileID: 6253049638512766740, guid: 4201256a4ededc34280673d4b190f5e3, type: 3}
    - Id: lucky
      Prefab: {fileID: 6253049638512766740, guid: 56c43cb5b51ef194dacd9114181abf8a, type: 3}
    - Id: rich
      Prefab: {fileID: 6253049638512766740, guid: 9f73199c6f5180e43b5b0ec2f4081410, type: 3}
    - Id: three
      Prefab: {fileID: 6253049638512766740, guid: 4cc8fecd86db8eb4b925bb7eadd823a0, type: 3}
    - Id: fish
      Prefab: {fileID: 6253049638512766740, guid: cf93f73e335db0443a3d4f0cfe047a83, type: 3}
    - Id: lotos
      Prefab: {fileID: 6253049638512766740, guid: a379973f381761146b63c3c42b5bf73a, type: 3}
    - Id: cat
      Prefab: {fileID: 6253049638512766740, guid: 2616fa9a1f2e3a447a85e88a44552442, type: 3}
    - Id: bird
      Prefab: {fileID: 6253049638512766740, guid: e4fc730c74c80b54cb1a777153271378, type: 3}
    - Id: money
      Prefab: {fileID: 6253049638512766740, guid: 177179d175c2a6c49b6de20f97313ae2, type: 3}
    Stages:
    - StageIndex: 1
      LayoutLevel: 1
      UseCustomLayout: 0
      CustomSlots: []
      Background: {fileID: -1071225944978810969, guid: 51b6c3abe2f45de468edcc148a432b81, type: 3}
      Title: Mahjong
      Description: "Mahjong, 19. y\xFCzy\u0131lda \xC7in\u2019de \xE7ok oyunculu
        stratejik bir masa oyunu olarak ortaya \xE7\u0131km\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r,
        ancak zamanla mekanikleri tek oyunculu formata uyarlanm\u0131\u015F ve bizim
        oyunumuz da bu versiyonu temel alm\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r."
    - StageIndex: 2
      LayoutLevel: 2
      UseCustomLayout: 0
      CustomSlots: []
      Background: {fileID: 6739164850763713329, guid: abeb88fb0fef3f04390e9599c265a636, type: 3}
      Title: Seviye 2
      Description: "Orijinal Mahjong\u2019da ama\xE7 ta\u015F kombinasyonlar\u0131
        olu\u015Fturmakt\u0131r, fakat bu mant\u0131k solitaire (tek oyunculu) versiyonda
        e\u015Fle\u015Fen ta\u015Flar\u0131 bulup kald\u0131rma sistemine d\xF6n\xFC\u015Fm\xFC\u015Ft\xFCr
        ve bu sistem bizim oyunumuzda da kullan\u0131lmaktad\u0131r."
    - StageIndex: 3
      LayoutLevel: 3
      UseCustomLayout: 0
      CustomSlots: []
      Background: {fileID: -2944664853789933741, guid: b2d1b590becb1764b852ddc4ba45bb21, type: 3}
      Title: 
      Description: "Klasik Mahjong ta\u015Flar\u0131 kendine \xF6zg\xFC semboller
        ve g\xF6rsel farkl\u0131l\u0131klar i\xE7erir; bu \xF6zellik bizim oyunumuzda
        da korunarak oyuncunun ta\u015Flar\u0131 h\u0131zl\u0131 tan\u0131mas\u0131
        ve e\u015Fle\u015Ftirmesi sa\u011Flan\u0131r."
    - StageIndex: 4
      LayoutLevel: 4
      UseCustomLayout: 0
      CustomSlots: []
      Background: {fileID: 1003138819240211484, guid: 3b99f403a09d5214eaa07cf4c3c6de9a, type: 3}
      Title: 
      Description: "Geleneksel Mahjong\u2019da masay\u0131 do\u011Fru okuyabilmek
        ve mevcut hamleleri analiz edebilmek \xE7ok \xF6nemlidir; ayn\u0131 prensip
        bizim oyunumuzda \u201Ca\xE7\u0131k ta\u015Flar\u201D mekani\u011Fi ile uygulanmaktad\u0131r."
    - StageIndex: 5
      LayoutLevel: 5
      UseCustomLayout: 0
      CustomSlots: []
      Background: {fileID: -1071225944978810969, guid: 51b6c3abe2f45de468edcc148a432b81, type: 3}
      Title: 
      Description: "Tarihsel olarak Mahjong ta\u015Flar\u0131 masada katmanl\u0131
        \u015Fekilde dizilirdi ve bu \xE7ok katmanl\u0131 yap\u0131, bizim oyunumuzdaki
        seviyelerin derinlik ve zorluk sisteminin temelini olu\u015Fturur."
    - StageIndex: 6
      LayoutLevel: 6
      UseCustomLayout: 0
      CustomSlots: []
      Background: {fileID: 6860068949404887012, guid: 39ff397a0622edc4fa4d86c02f5fdfb2, type: 3}
      Title: 
      Description: "Mahjong, \xE7ocuklar ve yeti\u015Fkinler i\xE7in haf\u0131zay\u0131,
        dikkat s\xFCresini ve g\xF6rsel alg\u0131y\u0131 geli\u015Ftiren g\xFC\xE7l\xFC
        bir zihinsel egzersiz olarak kabul edilir."
    - StageIndex: 7
      LayoutLevel: 7
      UseCustomLayout: 0
      CustomSlots: []
      Background: {fileID: 4110671742852751834, guid: 3e5a6e364e8bed941bb6bfabc8c12526, type: 3}
      Title: 
      Description: "D\xFCzenli olarak Mahjong oynamak, \xF6zellikle \xE7ocuklarda
        problem \xE7\xF6zme becerilerini ve sab\u0131rl\u0131 d\xFC\u015F\xFCnme
        al\u0131\u015Fkanl\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131 geli\u015Ftirmeye yard\u0131mc\u0131
        olur."
    - StageIndex: 8
      LayoutLevel: 8
      UseCustomLayout: 0
      CustomSlots: []
      Background: {fileID: -497180305073538546, guid: 92fce6fc1d6dfe242a88a9a972ffee4d, type: 3}
      Title: 
      Description: "Klasik Mahjong dikkat, haf\u0131za ve analiz gerektirir; bizim
        oyunumuzda da oyuncu s\xFCrekli olarak sahay\u0131 tarar, e\u015Fle\u015Fmeleri
        bulur ve hamlelerini planlar, bu da zihinsel aktiviteyi art\u0131r\u0131r."
    - StageIndex: 9
      LayoutLevel: 9
      UseCustomLayout: 0
      CustomSlots: []
      Background: {fileID: -810623022255831621, guid: 5adc178a21b7bcb4b8321019ae6bcb49, type: 3}
      Title: 
      Description: "Bizim oyunumuzda her seviye farkl\u0131 yerle\u015Fimler ve g\xF6rsel
        kombinasyonlar sundu\u011Fu i\xE7in oyuncunun beyni s\xFCrekli yeni desenlere
        adapte olur, bu da \xF6\u011Frenme ve odaklanma yetene\u011Fini g\xFC\xE7lendirir."
    - StageIndex: 10
      LayoutLevel: 10
      UseCustomLayout: 0
      CustomSlots: []
      Background: {fileID: 7258380301350862247, guid: ba0c54380548b5a40a547440220c7b01, type: 3}
      Title: 
      Description: "Mahjong tarih boyunca farkl\u0131 k\xFClt\xFCrlere ve teknolojilere
        uyum sa\u011Flayarak geli\u015Fmi\u015Ftir; bizim oyunumuz ise bu evrimin
        modern bir par\xE7as\u0131 olarak, mobil ve \xF6l\xE7eklenebilir bir yap\u0131
        ile \xD6z Game platformuna entegre edilmi\u015Ftir."
